## AI discovery needs strong source material.

Gemini and similar tools need content that is specific, consistent and trustworthy. Thin pages and generic claims are weak signals.

Focus on clear expertise, structured answers, updated pages, schema and content that explains your unique approach.

## The practical checklist

Build topic hubs, answer real questions, add proof, maintain technical SEO, and keep your brand information consistent across the web.
